Date:   Wed Mar 25 10:23:54 2026 -0500

    fix: handle signal-killed processes in CLI integration test

    The status test silently swallowed signal kills (status=null) from CI
    resource pressure, producing empty stdout and a confusing assertion
    error. Now detects signal kills, retries once, and reports clearly.

    Entire-Checkpoint: 3a6818c0f7d3

diff --git a/src/commands/cli.integration.test.ts b/src/commands/cli.integration.test.ts
index 2c90712..d4f86be 100644
--- a/src/commands/cli.integration.test.ts
+++ b/src/commands/cli.integration.test.ts
@@ -67,27 +67,44 @@ describe("CLI version integration", () => {
   });

